title: Annie Potts / Broken Bones
description: Sitting in a tree, K-I-S-S-I-N-G! Sean reveals his childhood celebrity crush. Priyanka talks about traveling to Georgia to perform her one woman show for medical students. Annie Potts is on the show is discuss the scary car crash she was in and her recovery since.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
